                <h4>Open Positions:</h4>
                <h4 class="highlight">Undergraduate Biology Research Assistant (Internship)</h4>
                <p>
                    To apply for a posted position, please email your CV to <a href="https://html.modernwebtemplates.com/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="402832002332292e25342923336e232f2d">[email&#160;protected]</a> along with a cover letter outlining how you are a fit for the position. We review all CVs submitted for posted positions, but we are unable to respond individually to all
